== Urugomero rwa Rusumo ==
Urugomero rwa Rusumo<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/article/urugomero-rwa-rusumo-ruratanga-amashanyarazi-mu-mpera-z-uyu-mwaka</ref>ni u Rugomero rwubatswe kubufatanye bwibihugu birimo Rwanda Burundi na Tanzania. 

ni urugomero rwitezweho ko ruzatanga MEGEWATI 80 zigomba gusangira ibi bihugu

[[Rwanda|U rwanda]] U burundi  ndetse na Tanzania<ref>https://www.eac.int/eac-partner-states/tanzania</ref> kuko byose bisangiye umugezi wa Akagera

== Ubwubatsi ==
ni Urugomero rwubatse numushinga NELSAP-CU (Nile Equatorial Lakes Subsidary Action Program-Coordination Unit),<ref>https://nelsap.nilebasin.org/index.php/en/</ref>

uyumushinga uvugako urugomero rwadindijwe na Covid 19 ariko ubu imirimo yo kurusoza irimbanyije igeze kukigero cya 79%

